{"pid":"ee48b03fe44d7c5be5218ba6acee1878ba91b9fe","tid":321964,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"貓BB會追打咬同伴，從而綀習捕獵<br />\n貓仔當你同伴所以咬你<br />\n你嚮佢咬你時要大聲喝止，然後立刻攞玩具同佢玩具（吊吊下果d老鼠）<br />\n久而久之佢就知道玩捕獵遊戲要同玩具玩，唔可以同人玩"},{"pid":"0f33d97bbbb7c1b30d7c2fdfeec805a49e1cd259","tid":321964,"uid":13871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓BB會追打咬同伴，從而綀習捕獵<br />\n貓仔當你同伴所以咬你<br />\n你嚮佢咬你時要大聲喝止，然後立刻攞玩具同佢玩具（吊吊下果d老鼠）<br />\n久而久之佢就知道玩捕獵遊戲要同玩具玩，唔可以同人玩</blockquote><br />\n我試吓先 真係好想摸下佢 但係佢次次咬到我真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3edf4d5eebd761c1fed1b9f0347b6e74f2d6d6","tid":321964,"uid":53694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"叫你隻貓做張志明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真 我都想知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615be5b9dfbaef252886598eee60c8046cc179a1","tid":321964,"uid":13871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你隻貓做張志明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真 我都想知點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到絲打個po 同一命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb9fd23b082cbdee5f9334fed198ae4e7bd4bb8","tid":321964,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"我以前佢咬我<br />\n我把佢成個頭塞入我個口食佢<br />\n佢會好驚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢爪我<br />\n我會打到佢趴係到<br />\n<br />\n佢宜家一直都好乖<br />\n成日同我一齊訓<i